# ── Optional providers ───────────────────────────────────────────────
# Draftly works fully on real Riot Data Dragon data with no config.
# Set these only to connect live meta stats (win/pick/ban/counters).

# URL of a backend/serverless endpoint that returns normalised meta stats
# (see src/data/providers/meta/httpMeta.ts for the expected JSON shape).
# Leave unset to run attribute-only analysis with meta shown as "not connected".
# VITE_META_API_URL=https://your-proxy.example.com/api/meta

# Data Dragon locale (default en_US)
# VITE_DDRAGON_LOCALE=en_US
